Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Foreign policy wobbles
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1n8
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Mar 1980
New foreign policy wobble as US cites 'mistake' on voting intentions over Israel. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less